OL,3,CThunderstorm warning issued as humid
OL,4,Cweather continues
OL,6,FThe Met Office has issued a yellow
OL,7,Fwarning for thunderstorms in Wales
OL,8,Fthroughout Thursday, with parts of the
OL,9,Fsouth east of England advised they
OL,10,Fcould also see some thunder on
OL,11,FWednesday.
OL,13,FMeteorologist at the Met Office, Becky
OL,14,FMitchell, said: "The heat and humidity
OL,15,Fwe've got across England and Wales is
OL,16,Fgoing to spark off some thundery
OL,17,Fshowers on Wednesday and Thursday so
OL,18,Fwe've got some yellow weather warnings
OL,19,Fin force.
