OL,3,CThunderstorm warning issued as humid
OL,4,Cweather continues
OL,6,F"There is a risk of flooding on
OL,7,FThursday afternoon in some parts of
OL,8,Fthe country, but the thunderstorms
OL,9,Fwill be "quite hit and miss."
OL,11,FThe Met Office said Thursday afternoon
OL,12,Fcould see 50 to 100mm of rain in a few
OL,13,Fhours in some spots, which is more
OL,14,Fthan a month's worth of rainfall.
OL,16,FThe heat is not set to last into the
OL,17,Fweekend as temperatures are expected
OL,18,Fto return to the mid-20s in the south
OL,19,Fas a band of rain moves through the
OL,20,Fcountry on Saturday.
