OL,3,CThunderstorm warning issued as humid
OL,4,Cweather continues
OL,6,FTo cope with warm evenings, the Met
OL,7,FOffice has urged Britons to keep their
OL,8,Fhomes as cool as possible.
OL,10,FOfficial advice said: "Overnight
OL,11,Ftemperatures are going to be very high
OL,12,Fso it's quite hard to cool houses down
OL,13,Fin that situation because you don't
OL,14,Fhave the relief overnight and
OL,15,Ftemperatures dropping.
OL,17,F"If you can open your windows at
OL,18,Fnight, try to let some of the cooler
OL,19,Fair in and keep curtains or blinds
OL,20,Fshut during the day".
